    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, ready to hit the road with its next owner! It drives smoothly and has been well-cared for over the years. It's perfect if you're looking for a dependable vehicle that's ready to go. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and tell you more about it!",
