    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver's example featuring the legendary 3.2L S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Engineered for the purist, this chassis has been addressed for common platform weak points: the rear subframe has been reinforced, the VANOS system overhauled, and rod bearings replaced for peace of mind. The high-revving powerplant pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline, supported by a factory variable M-differential lock and a taut suspension setup. While the exterior shows minor signs of use consistent with its 'good' condition, the drivetrain and throttle response remain razor-sharp. A technically sound investment for those who value performance and preventative maintenance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Clean title. Routine maintenance records included. Minor cosmetic wear only. Engine and transmission perform well. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 34000.0,
