      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for the road? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is looking for a new home. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
